<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1112,1189,1981,2002]" pageId="10" pageNumber="33" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, in dorsal and lateral views (left paramere missing), scale = 0.1 mm; (14) ditto, paramere in ventral view, scale = 0.05 mm; (15) ditto, internal sac in dorsal view, scale = 0.05 mm.
</paragraph>
